    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride for me\u2014super reliable and still handles the road like a pro. It\u2019s in great shape and has been really well-loved, so you\u2019re getting a solid vehicle that\u2019s ready for plenty more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable set of wheels that won\u2019t let you down, this is the one. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
