    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 996 Carrera featuring the 3.4L water-cooled flat-six and a precision 6-speed manual transaxle. This example boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and RMS replacement, addressing critical preventative maintenance. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the platform's legendary turn-in and mid-corner stability. Engine compression is strong across all cylinders, delivering linear power through the rev range. The hydraulic steering rack provides the tactile feedback modern EPS lacks. Finished in Arctic Silver over black leather, this driver-focused Porsche presents in honest, well-sorted condition for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
